{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_05_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 僕達との約束",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― On the day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1280.0000191000001,
          "startTime": 1.2800000191
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ。僕らは準備出来たよ\nお客さんは……うん、しっかり入ってるみたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey there. We're all set.\nIt looks like the audience is filling up nicely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、年末の大きなライブだからな\nひとまずは安心だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's a big year-end live after all.\nFor now‚ we can breathe easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "心配なんかしてたの？　僕らの出るライブなのに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you really worried? It's our show‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.0666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんが少ない、なんてあり得ないよ\n君は変なところで心配性だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way we'd have a small audience.\nYou're such a worrywart in strange places.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなんじゃ、体が持たないよ\nすぐ胃を悪くしそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With that attitude‚\nyour stomach won't hold up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4333326657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに心配し過ぎだったかもしれないな\nでも、ライブの成否の責任は俺にもあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might be right. I might have worried too much.\nBut I also share the responsibility for the success of the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.799999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、それもそうだね。ただ、その点で言えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's true. But when it comes to that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4666659991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2333331744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "君はもう、とっくに\n責任を全うしてくれてると思うけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been fulfilling your responsibilities\nfor a while now‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3333331744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺が？　もう全うしている？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me? Already fulfilling them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "この前の、ジュエリーの広告モデルだよ\nあれは確かに手応えがあった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm talking about that jewelry ad work you did earlier.\nYou definitely made an impact there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6709674906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.9666665077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "あの仕事を機にリズノワは\n他の広告の仕事でも表に立つことが増えたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that work‚ LizNoir\nstarted appearing in other ads‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "オファーをもらうこともあれば\n味を占めた君が積極的に仕事を取ってきてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes I get an offer\nYou‚ who dominated the taste‚ actively took jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0999997456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "そうして何度も表に立てたからこそ\n今日のお客さんの動員にも影響が出ている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because we've put it out there so many times\nthat it's having an impact on audience today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.3000044187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "そのきっかけを作ってくれた時点で\n君はもう、責任を全うしてくれているってことさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the time you created that opportunity\nYou've already fulfilled your responsibility.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0333377521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえるのなら、頑張った甲斐があったよ\n葵自身も、なんだかんだで楽しそうだったしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so‚ it feels like my hard work paid off.\nPlus‚ it seemed like you were having fun‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6000043233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "楽しめたこともそうだし……いろいろ勉強にもなったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did enjoy it… and I learned quite a bit too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9333377521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3333377521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "自分に出来ることとかやれることって\n案外、自分で気付いてないものなんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that there are things I can do…\nThings I can contribute that I hadn't realized before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして霧子も\nあの頃はそんな風に考えていたのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Maybe even Kiriko\nfelt the same way back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4000043233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.5333377521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さん？　……そうか\nバンプロにいた頃はあの人が見てたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeko-san? …I see.\nBack when we were in Van Prods.‚ she was watching over us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.2000044187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "うん。興味もないような仕事を取ってきては\nリズノワを売るためにも受けるべきってうるさくてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ she kept pushing us to take on jobs that didn't interest us at all.\nShe said we should take them to promote LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "僕も莉央も、必要ないって突っぱねてた\nチャレンジしようって気持ちすら抱かなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both I and Rio rejected them‚ even challenged them…\nWe didn't have the motivation back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "あの人を擁護するつもりなんて一ミリもないよ\nやり方は気に食わないし、間違ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no intention of defending that person in the slightest.\nI don't like how she did it‚ and it was wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1000166257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "でも……自分達を売り込むことは大事だった\nそのためにはライブ以外の仕事もこなさないといけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… She wasn't wrong about promoting ourselves.\nTo do that‚ we have to do work other than live shows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1000165303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "その点に限れば\n霧子の方針は、何も間違ってなかったんだなって思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As far as that point goes\nI don't think there was anything wrong with Kiriko's policy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.266683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.7666832924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どんなにパフォーマンスが優れていても\n認知してもらわなければ、見せつけることは出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how great our performance is‚\nif we're not recognized‚ we can't make an impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.6000165303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今回の仕事が、そのいい機会になったってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this job was a good opportunity for that‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1000166257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.1333499591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "そういうこと。ただ、君と霧子が明確に違う点は……\n君があの人ほど非道にはなれないお人好しってこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. But there's a clear difference between you and Himeko…\nYou're not as ruthless as she was. You're too kind-hearted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.466683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あのな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh come on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.0333499591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.4666832924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、君と、君が持ってきた仕事を信頼出来たし\n僕自身が納得して仕事をこなせたってことさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I trusted you and the jobs you brought in.\nAnd because I trusted‚ I could perform with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.166683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.2666832924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirにとって間違いなくプラスになった\n……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without a doubt‚ you've been a plus for LizNoir.\n…Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.4943937461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.9666853269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "葵……。どういたしまして\nでも俺は、当然のことをしたまでだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi… You're welcome.\nBut I'll continue to do what's expected of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.7000165303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.5333519936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあこれからも、その当然を、よろしく頼むよ\n来年は本気で、頂点を取りにいく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ from now on‚ I'll rely on you to do what's expected.\nNext year‚ we're going all out to reach the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "それに、君が全力でバックアップしてくれれば……\n君にもトップの景色を見せてあげられるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And with your full support…\nI can show you the view from the top too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.1831242584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.2000186603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それはぜひ期待したいところだな\n……楽しみにしてるから、任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll definitely look forward to that.\n…I'm counting on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 238.9666853269
    },
    {
