      "startTime": 244.2500125568
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.2500125568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今日は来てくれてありがとう\n今年も応援してくれたこと、心から感謝してる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for coming today.\nI truly appreciate your support throughout this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2566.6726747000157,
          "startTime": 247.8666852315
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "なかなか思った結果が出せなくて、悔しくて\nみんなをがっかりさせたこともあるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We might not have achieved the results we hoped for‚\nand we might have disappointed some of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.4000165303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 263.3333458901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "でも――来年は違う\nいろんなことに挑戦して、劇的に成長して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… next year will be different.\nWe'll take on various challenges and grow dramatically…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.0000185649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi029.m4a",
      "text": "誰にも文句を言わせないぐらい\n圧倒的に格好いいLizNoirへ進化するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the point where no one can complain…\nWe'll evolve into an incredibly cool LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.5000185649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 277.8000125568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_03-aoi030.m4a",
      "text": "だから、心待ちにしていてほしい\n――僕達との、約束だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please look forward to it.\n―― It's our promise with you.",
        "id": ""
